When I became a mom my life changed. I wondered if things would go back to normal, but nothing was the same. Then one day I looked in the mirror and realized, I had changed. My priorities. My hopes. My worries. My interest. My boundaries. My world was all new and it has never been more beautiful 🌸🤎 Happy Mother’s Day to all the amazing women in my life. #boymom
